OL,3,CVaping, verbal abuse and truancy
OL,4,Cproblems found in many Welsh secondary
OL,5,Cschools
OL,7,FA national campaign is needed to help
OL,8,Ftackle bad behaviour in schools,
OL,9,Faccording to Wales' schools
OL,10,Finspections body Estyn.
OL,12,FIn a report, based on visits to 24
OL,13,Fsecondary schools and discussions with
OL,14,Flocal authorities, vaping, persistent
OL,15,Fdisruption and truancy were all
OL,16,Fidentified as issues.
OL,18,FIt comes as the Welsh Government is
OL,19,Fset to hold a summit to discuss
OL,20,Fbehaviour with teachers in the summer.
