OL,3,CVaping, verbal abuse and truancy
OL,4,Cproblems found in many Welsh secondary
OL,5,Cschools
OL,7,FIn lessons, school staff said pupils
OL,8,Fanswered the teacher back or
OL,9,Fdisrespected staff, and refused to
OL,10,Fcomplete work, and there were
OL,11,Finstances of verbal abuse towards
OL,12,Fpupils and staff.
OL,14,FThere were also increasing reports of
OL,15,Fmobile phone misuse and corridor
OL,16,Fmisbehaviour.
