OL,3,CVaping, verbal abuse and truancy
OL,4,Cproblems found in many Welsh secondary
OL,5,Cschools
OL,7,FTeaching staff voiced concerns that
OL,8,Fmanaging behaviour took up a
OL,9,Fsignificant amount of their teaching
OL,10,Ftime, often affecting the quality of
OL,11,Flearning for all pupils.
OL,13,FThe main poor behaviours seen outside
OL,14,Fof lessons, during unsupervised times,
OL,15,Fwere vaping, use of mobile phones
OL,16,Fagainst school policy and damage to
OL,17,Fschool property, in particular toilets.
