OL,4,Cproblems found in many Welsh secondary
OL,5,Cschools
OL,7,FA number of schools even reported
OL,8,Fdefiance from some parents in adhering
OL,9,Fto school policies. Nearly all schools
OL,10,Fnoted a degree of difficulty in
OL,11,Fengaging with some parents about
OL,12,Fbehavioural issues. These parents
OL,13,Foften challenged the schools'
OL,14,Fexpectations around behaviour and
OL,15,Fnoted that they struggled to manage
OL,16,Ftheir children's behaviour at home.
