OL,7,FIn the national survey, many staff
OL,8,Fdescribed some parents as
OL,9,Funsupportive, sometimes undermining
OL,10,Fstaff by excusing poor behaviour. Some
OL,11,Fparents displayed aggressive behaviour
OL,12,Ftowards leaders and staff when
OL,13,Fpresented with concerns.
