OL,3,CVaping, verbal abuse and truancy
OL,4,Cproblems found in many Welsh secondary
OL,5,Cschools
OL,7,FSome pupils said readjusting to school
OL,8,Flife after the Covid pandemic had been
OL,9,Fchallenging, in particular
OL,10,Festablishing relationships with their
OL,11,Fpeers and staff, while others said
OL,12,Ftheir poor behaviour in school was
OL,13,Fbecause of difficulties they had at
OL,14,Fhome.
OL,16,FSome school leaders expressed concern
OL,17,Fabout the growing impact of socio-
OL,18,Feconomic pressures, mental health
OL,19,Fneeds, and a lack of timely specialist
OL,20,Fsupport.
