OL,3,CVaping, verbal abuse and truancy
OL,4,Cproblems found in many Welsh secondary
OL,5,Cschools
OL,7,FThe national survey also revealed that
OL,8,Fstaff felt there was a lack of
OL,9,Ftargeted support for pupils with
OL,10,Fadditional learning needs, including
OL,11,Fthose with ADHD, leading to challenges
OL,12,Fin lessons.
OL,14,FMany local authorities shared that
OL,15,Fchallenges remained, including an
OL,16,Fincrease in the number of exclusions
OL,17,Fand higher demand from schools for
OL,18,Fsupport for pupils and staff.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/13
