OL,3,CVaping, verbal abuse and truancy
OL,4,Cproblems found in many Welsh secondary
OL,5,Cschools
OL,7,FThe challenges identified by local
OL,8,Fauthorities were poor family
OL,9,Fengagement with schools, verbal abuse
OL,10,Ftowards school staff which included
OL,11,Fthreatening behaviour, mobile phone
OL,12,Fuse in school, problems arising from
OL,13,Fsocial media, vaping on the school
OL,14,Fsite particularly in toilets, internal
OL,15,Ftruancy, high anxiety and an increase
OL,16,Fin ALN referrals, particularly around
OL,17,Fneurodiversity.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/13
