OL,3,CVaping, verbal abuse and truancy
OL,4,Cproblems found in many Welsh secondary
OL,5,Cschools
OL,7,FChief inspector Owen Evans said:
OL,8,F"Pupil behaviour can be challenging
OL,9,Fand positive behaviour doesn't just
OL,10,Fhappen ` it's the result of strong and
OL,11,Fcompassionate leadership allied to
OL,12,Fclear and consistently applied
OL,13,Fbehaviour management, consistent staff
OL,14,Ftraining and involves the support of
OL,15,Fthe whole school community.
