OL,3,CVaping, verbal abuse and truancy
OL,4,Cproblems found in many Welsh secondary
OL,5,Cschools
OL,7,F"Our report shows that schools that
OL,8,Fprioritise well-being, establish high
OL,9,Fexpectations, and build trusting
OL,10,Frelationships with families are more
OL,11,Flikely to succeed in creating safe and
OL,12,Fsupportive learning environments. We
OL,13,Fwant this report to serve as a
OL,14,Fplatform to promote the effective and
OL,15,Fpositive practices we've seen in
OL,16,Fschools across Wales."
