OL,7,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"We are committed to ensuring
OL,9,Feverything possible is done to address
OL,10,Fdeclining behaviour in schools and
OL,11,Fcolleges. Making sure learners and
OL,12,Fstaff feel safe and supported in our
OL,13,Feducational settings is essential.
