OL,7,F"We welcome this important report from
OL,8,FEstyn which both highlights the issues
OL,9,Four secondary schools are facing and,
OL,10,Fimportantly, the steps that can be
OL,11,Ftaken to address them. We will be
OL,12,Fdiscussing these points further at our
OL,13,Fbehaviour summit later this month,
OL,14,Fwhere we will also reflect on today's
OL,15,Froundtable on violence and safety in
OL,16,Fschools and colleges."
